<p><strong>在万圣节寻找南瓜是否搞错了什么</strong></p>
<p><strong>发布时间：</strong>2020年11月1日</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605432796" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span>，进入<a href="/lyricslinn-s-personnel-file">人事档案</a>查看该名作者的更多作品</p>
<p><strong>中心：</strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/linkage-hub">linkAge</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
